reviewText: I must say its every hard to recommend this but i understand to each there own, I like hentai which makes it weird that I have a stronger dislike for rape or acts that are close to it. This anime hit every bullet point for me not to want to watch it but one; No Tentacle scenes (Which is the only reason it didn't get a 1/5. Its 2 dist and the dvd production seems higher than most dvds found on Amazon. Also the first dvds art is very dated, if i have the time i'll try and post a clean pictures of it, if amazon lets me.This may not be a problem for any one but me, there only english dub or japanese dub with englsih subs. I was hoping for engilsh dub & subs but thats a small drop in the bucket are problem i have with this animeOn the plus the story i would not say is good but it seems they put a lot of thought in to it, way more than any other hentai ive seen, For a long time "Story Wise" I thought "The Hills Have Size" was number one but this seems to blow that a way. Again I'm not saying its good but thought full. Buy it if your in to extreme scenes but if your a soft core (Even mid) please stay away.
